Bug Tracker Project Plan

Objective

Develop an offline-first Android Bug Tracker application using Kotlin.

Architecture

- MVVM
- Repository Pattern
- Room Database
- Retrofit
- WorkManager for synchronization

Features

- Create Bug
- Read Bug
- Update Bug
- Delete Bug
- Offline Storage
- Automatic Sync
- Retry Failed Sync
- Git Version Control

Development Phases

1. Project Setup
2. Room Database
3. Retrofit API
4. Repository
5. ViewModel
6. User Interface
7. Offline Synchronization
8. Testing
9. Release
